Others: The Houston Astros secured the AL West division title by defeating the Arizona Diamondbacks.
The Texas Rangers needed a victory or a Houston Astros loss to secure the AL West, but the Seattle Mariners played spoiler, taking down the Rangers 1-0.
The defending World Series champions, the Houston Astros, will have an automatic berth in the ALDS.
The Wild Card Round matchups have been determined: Minnesota will host Toronto and Tampa Bay will host Texas in the AL, while Milwaukee will host Arizona and Philadelphia will host Miami in the NL.
